latestPosts.caption:
|| Good Day (I'm Tired) Director's cut ||

This was a special project for us as it was our first attempt at a full fledged music video, with the responsibility of direction, cinematography and post production. With all the creative freedom that we had, we got the opportunity to implement whatever skills and knowledge we'd acquired in the past few months. We got a great response on YouTube but we'll definitely come up with something even better next time.
Thank you all for supporting us :)
_______________________________________________________
